  "body": "Reproducing on IOS 16.6, iPhone X\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Open any chat\r\n2. Paste data containing links into composer\r\nExample of data: \r\n```\r\nResolved preview \r\nBsbd\r\nSbdb\r\nHShs\r\nShshS\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15253\r\n\r\nhttps://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Je7yErjEVt4\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OYjZK_6i37M&pp=ygUIZ29kc21hY2s%3D\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/Mp0jlNquSnM\r\n\r\nhttps://bit.ly/41ScFYY\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/Beb8cktBTxY\r\n```\r\n3. Close the composer\r\n4. Remove links previews from composer\r\n5. Expand the composer\r\n6. Try to scroll data in the input field to the bottom\r\n7. Observe the result\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** unable to scroll to the bottom\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97245802/c06c0bbd-e63d-4ed7-b10c-e8a516f30a4a\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** able to scroll to the bottom\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
